data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat on Long Lake in Michigan! This picturesque ranch-style home boasts three spacious bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a full basement for all your storage needs or fix the way you want. With 135 feet of frontage, you'll enjoy breathtaking views of the tranquil waters right from your doorstep. The property includes a generously sized lot across the road, perfect for outdoor activities or potential expansion. Park your vehicles in the convenient two-car attached garage, and soak in the serenity from the expansive deck overlooking the lake. Whether you're seeking a peaceful getaway or a year-round residence, this waterfront oasis offers the ultimate in comfort and relaxation.
